            <div type="transcript" id="J1278">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Mountains stood in Haze --</l>
                    <l>The Valleys stopped below</l>
                    <l>And went or waited as they liked</l>
                    <l>The River and the Sky.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>At leisure was the Sun --</l>
                    <l>His interests of Fire</l>
                    <l>A little from remark withdrawn --</l>
                    <l>The Twilight spoke the Spire,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>So soft upon the Scene</l>
                    <l>The Act of evening fell</l>
                    <l>We felt how neighborly a Thing</l>
                    <l>Was the Invisible.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>9. Scene) Place</l>
                </lg>

